{
  "texts": [
    "Dispatcher The dispatcher distributes inference requests from clients to their respective workers.",
    "It first fetches the client-DNN mapping from the scheduler and then redirects the requests to the workers running the corresponding DNNs.",
    "The dispatcher also handles all the connections to clients and includes service endpoints to interact with the clients, e.g., to (de)register clients in the system.",
    "Worker Each worker is statically allocated on one GPU and maintains a local queue to buffer incoming requests.",
    "The worker process batches requests (resizing them if needed) in the queue and sends the request batches to the DNN deployed on the GPU for execution."
  ]
}